{"tid":257741,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港影視史上最深入民心嘅奸角/反派係?","createTime":"2017-05-25T13:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T10:10:09.000Z","uid":118314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84608caf35e02d29176c1575795d451c287e1ceb","tid":257741,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"一套作品入面，主角往往係正義嘅一方，而奸角只能係配角。<br />\n然而，一套成功嘅影視作品，除咗擁有受歡迎嘅主角，一定有更受歡迎嘅奸角。 曾經諗過，但唔敢做嘅事;<br />\n奸角往往有戈句講戈句，想要呢樣野就點都要得到手;<br />\n同滿口正義嘅主角相比，何嘗不是一種吸引力? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因此，今次想同大家討論一下香港影視史嘅奸角。<br />\n各位覺得，最深入民心嘅奸角係邊個? 邊個演得最出色，令你好想衝入個mon打9佢嘅同時，又不得不佩服佢嘅氣勢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係近年講起「奸角」二字一定會諗起，奸到出汁嘅鄭子誠?<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20121003/large/1349241066_0ff6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20121003%2Flarge%2F1349241066_0ff6.jpg&h=0558871f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係一代奸角「奸人堅」石堅?<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20090605/large/05ec1p4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20090605%2Flarge%2F05ec1p4a.jpg&h=8d92afc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係變態殺人狂黃秋生?<br />\n<img src=\"http://look.atmovies.com.tw/eweekly/ew000/v389/images/x3-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flook.atmovies.com.tw%2Feweekly%2Few000%2Fv389%2Fimages%2Fx3-3.jpg&h=5e4988ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「惡人之首」何家駒?<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2015/07/25/php7tSy3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2015%2F07%2F25%2Fphp7tSy3z.jpg&h=2e1cebc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係佢眼中所有人都係<del>雞</del>垃圾嘅斷水流大師兄?<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/stock2012/1412427487-1104710478_n.jpg?v=1412427489\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fstock2012%2F1412427487-1104710478_n.jpg%3Fv%3D1412427489&h=8f483d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日諗起你老婆嘅童星譚真一?<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160806/large/1470497498_0f41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160806%2Flarge%2F1470497498_0f41.jpg&h=a86595b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係騙徒吳良榮?<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20151121/photo/bkn-20151121165111544-1121_00862_001_07p.jpg?20151121205419\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20151121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151121165111544-1121_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20151121205419&h=c047f537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n樓主無法一一盡錄，歡迎各位討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3232330f97acfaa779caff957afc44e90be30b","tid":257741,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"四大惡人"},{"pid":"5959cb5bbc8011d952d71b4734652e5a0aaf71b7","tid":257741,"uid":39192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:25:55.000Z","msg":"唐立言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af750322714175545a3707db08d0643c6dc5f3a","tid":257741,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唐立言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c5/Tong_lap_yin_dragon1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20081018094228\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc5%2FTong_lap_yin_